                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-370" type="surname" value="BRISEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-370" type="given" value="SARAH"></interp>SARAH BRISEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with my mother, who keeps a lodging-house in Randall-street, Limehouse—the prisoner lodged there nine weeks—I missed a ring and ear-rings from my own room—the prisoner was taken on another charge, and some duplicates found upon him—he said, "They belong to you, Sarah, but I shall get a ship and replace them to-morrow"—I had missed them about five weeks.</p>
